<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="27" type="materials_examined">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="27">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="27">
Russia. Prov. Sanct-Petersburg: 5 km australi-occidentum, 26 June 1997, N.N. Tzvelev N-257 (conserved type, designated by 
<bibRefCitation DOI="https://doi.org/10.2307/1224640" author="Soreng, RJ" journalOrPublisher="Taxon" pageId="0" pageNumber="27" pagination="157 - 159" refId="B20" refString="Soreng, RJ, Barrie, FR, 1999. (1391) Proposal to conserve the name Poa pratensis (Poaceae) with a conserved type. Taxon 48 (1): 157 - 159, DOI: https://doi.org/10.2307/1224640" title="(1391) Proposal to conserve the name Poa pratensis (Poaceae) with a conserved type." url="https://doi.org/10.2307/1224640" volume="48" year="1999">Soreng and Barrie 1999</bibRefCitation>
: 157: BM!; isotypes: B!, C!, CAN!, CONC!, H!, K!, KW!, L!, LE!, LIV!, MA!, MO!, MW!, NSW!, P!, PE!, PR!, S!, SI!, TNS!, US (US3456252!), W!).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
